{
  "id": "69e4987b2b57aebdfe6bc60b",
  "title": "自他境界の図",
  "created": 1776588926,
  "updated": 1776598902,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69e4987b2b57aebdfe6bc60b",
      "text": "自他境界の図",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776588926,
      "updated": 1776588926
    },
    {
      "id": "69e4987d000000000008da43",
      "text": "いつかの日記に載っていたが、見つからない[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776588926,
      "updated": 1776588945
    },
    {
      "id": "69e49891000000000008da46",
      "text": "\t車輪の再発明をしよう",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776588946,
      "updated": 1776588954
    },
    {
      "id": "69e49a04000000000008da53",
      "text": "  元の図は確かこんな感じ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776589317,
      "updated": 1776589317
    },
    {
      "id": "69e49a04000000000008da54",
      "text": "   [https://gyazo.com/a89b981a557eb1cfe32f354942d0ab5d]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776589317,
      "updated": 1776589317
    },
    {
      "id": "69e49a04000000000008da55",
      "text": "    上：左が踏み込みすぎ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776589317,
      "updated": 1776589317
    },
    {
      "id": "69e49a04000000000008da56",
      "text": "    中：程々に離れている",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776589317,
      "updated": 1776589317
    },
    {
      "id": "69e49a04000000000008da57",
      "text": "    下：右が踏み込みすぎ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776589317,
      "updated": 1776589317
    },
    {
      "id": "69e49899000000000008da47",
      "text": " \t黒い線が分かっている前提の図は相互理解を促進しない。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776588954,
      "updated": 1776589367
    },
    {
      "id": "69e49a43000000000008da59",
      "text": " \t\t紛争でありがちなのは両方とも「相手が攻めてきた」と主張するやつ。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776589380,
      "updated": 1776589405
    },
    {
      "id": "69e49a6c000000000008da5a",
      "text": " \t\t\tそういうことにしたいのではなくお互いに本気でそう思っている。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776589421,
      "updated": 1776589440
    },
    {
      "id": "69e49a09000000000008da58",
      "text": "  \t[https://gyazo.com/aa23515ffa62230f92ad86cd856e5523]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776589321,
      "updated": 1776589349
    },
    {
      "id": "69e4991d000000000008da49",
      "text": "  \t\t上：距離が離れている",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776589086,
      "updated": 1776589454
    },
    {
      "id": "69e49931000000000008da4a",
      "text": "  \t\t下：距離が近すぎる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776589106,
      "updated": 1776589454
    },
    {
      "id": "69e49a97000000000008da5e",
      "text": "   \t理想的な黒線を消してしまえば、近すぎる離れすぎるの2択になる。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776589464,
      "updated": 1776589476
    },
    {
      "id": "69e49aa4000000000008da5f",
      "text": " 動きを表す矢印をつける。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776589477,
      "updated": 1776589542
    },
    {
      "id": "69e49acb000000000008da60",
      "text": " \t[https://gyazo.com/bd1a658880a1dc9a516807a555a3919f]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776589516,
      "updated": 1776589783
    },
    {
      "id": "69e49bda000000000008da63",
      "text": " \tこれだと追う追われるみたいになるが、そんなにシンプルなものでもない。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776589787,
      "updated": 1776589833
    },
    {
      "id": "69e49c08000000000008da64",
      "text": " \t\t描かないほうが良かったかもしれない。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776589833,
      "updated": 1776589846
    },
    {
      "id": "69e49bd6000000000008da62",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776589783,
      "updated": 1776589783
    },
    {
      "id": "69e499e1000000000008da52",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776589281,
      "updated": 1776589444
    },
    {
      "id": "69e49a84000000000008da5b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776589444,
      "updated": 1776589444
    },
    {
      "id": "69e49912000000000008da48",
      "text": "[/nishio/自他境界][nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1776589075,
      "updated": 1776592301
    },
    {
      "id": "69e49884000000000008da45",
      "text": " ありがとう[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776588932,
      "updated": 1776598705
    },
    {
      "id": "69e4beb10000000000fc053f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776598706,
      "updated": 1776598898
    },
    {
      "id": "69e4bf720000000000fc0543",
      "text": "これだこれ[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776598899,
      "updated": 1776598902
    },
    {
      "id": "69e4bebb0000000000fc0540",
      "text": " [/nishio/バウンダリーのタイプ]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776598715,
      "updated": 1776598895
    },
    {
      "id": "69e49883000000000008da44",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776588932,
      "updated": 1776588932
    }
  ]
}